- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses improving the performance of the maximum clique finder.
- cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) is another possibility as the paper analyzes networks from social domains and discusses the inter-relationships between network properties.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a less likely possibility, but still plausible as the paper discusses networks from biological and technological domains.
